# Generated by Cargo
# will have compiled files and executables
/target/

# Tauri-generated native projects (Android/iOS), regenerated by `tauri <platform> init`.
# Nothing here is committed. The release-signing delta is documented in desktop/README.md,
# and keystore.properties (signing secrets) lives here too and must never be committed.
/gen/

# Throwaway raster from `npm run gen:icon` (source is app-icon.svg; the generated
# set in icons/ is committed).
/app-icon.png
